Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.37,0:01:59.95,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't want to know!  思念是枷锁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.95,0:02:02.47,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't want to know!  後付けのlove
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.95,0:02:02.47,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't want to know!  追悔莫及的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.47,0:02:05.28,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't want to know!  優しさは仇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.47,0:02:05.28,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't want to know!  温柔是弱点
